Package: grafify
Type: Package
Title: A package for easy grafs, ANOVAs and posthoc comparisons
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Avinash R. Shenoy
Maintainer: The package maintainer <a.shenoy@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: This package makes it easy to plot graphs, has 8 colour-blind friendly colour schemes, and fits ordinary linear models or mixed effects models, and can perform post-hoc comparisons. It contains simple functions built mainly on ggplot2, lmerTest and emmeans. 
License: GPL
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0),
    ggplot2,
    lmerTest,
    emmeans
Imports: 
    purrr,
    Hmisc,
    tidyr,
    pbkrtest,
    stats
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2021-01-05
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/ashenoy-cmbi/grafify
